cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CC

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with language models and language representations. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves training a neural language model. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with neural models, and cs.CC (Computational Complexity) as it involves investigating correlations and causal relationships between language representations.
